# PromoImage Component Rules

## Overview
Rules for `src/components/atoms/PromoImage.tsx`

## Purpose
Atom that renders a responsive image inside an aspect-ratio container.

## Rules
- ✅ Props: `src` (required), `alt` (required), `aspectRatio?` (default `"16/13"`), `className?`.
- ✅ Layout: Wrapper `relative w-full rounded overflow-hidden` with native `style={{ aspectRatio }}`.
- ✅ Image: Use Next.js `<Image fill className="object-cover" priority />`.
- ✅ No dynamic Tailwind for aspect ratio (use CSS `aspect-ratio`).
- ✅ Export both named and default.

## Template
```tsx
<PromoImage src="/image.jpg" alt="Description" aspectRatio="16/9" />
```

## QA Checklist
- Image visible with correct alt text.
- Container respects provided `aspectRatio`.
- No CLS: image fills container without layout shift.